'''Baranor''' (b. {{FA|317}}) was a [[Men|man]] of the [[House of Bëor]].

== History ==
Baranor was the second son of [[Baran]] and grandson of [[Bëor]]. He had one son, [[Bereg]], who was born in {{FA|340}}.<ref name=WJBeor>{{WJ|14}}, ''(i) The House of Bëor''</ref>

